<p>
  {gettext(
    "When a channel is moderated, only operators (+o) and voiced (+v) users can send messages. Regular users can still read but not write."
  )}
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>{gettext("Usage")}</.help_h4>
<pre>{gettext("/mode +m — Enable moderated mode /mode -m — Disable moderated mode /mode +v Nick — Give voice to a user")}</pre>
